</ref> Avoidant and [[schizoid personality disorder|schizoid]] patterns were frequently confused or referred to synonymously until [[Ernst Kretschmer|Kretschmer]] (1921),<ref>{{Cite book
  | last = Kretschmer
  | first = Ernst
  | authorlink = Ernst Kretschmer
